            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="post/3455.html" rel="bookmark">[ Lumen 5.2 文档 ] 更多特性 —— 服务提供者</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-02-18T15:17:51+08:00">2016-02-18</time>
