                <a href="post/3437.html" rel="bookmark">[ Lumen 5.2 文档 ] 更多特性 —— 错误 &amp; 日志</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-02-17T21:16:26+08:00">2016-02-17</time>
