    <article id="post-3424" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="post/3424.html" rel="bookmark">[ Lumen 5.2 文档 ] 更多特性 —— 缓存</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-02-17T11:05:21+08:00">2016-02-17</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-02-17T11:05:45+08:00">2016-02-17 11:05:45</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    3565 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="post/3424.html#comments">
                        4 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="post/3424.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Lumen-1-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="post/3424.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="400" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Lumen-1-400x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、简介
Lumen为不同的缓存系统提供了统一的API。缓存配置项位于.env文件。在该文件中你可以指定在应用中默认使用哪个缓存驱动。Lumen支持目前流行的缓存系统如Memcached和Redis等。
2、和Laravel的区别
Lumen缓存驱动使用和Laravel一模一样的代码，除了配置之外，在Lumen和Laravel中使用缓存没有任何区别，因此，具体使用示例可参考完整的L...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
